entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the disabled Blacklight pirate and transfer the location of their leader to your ship. Then return to base while we plan the attack.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Try to find a Blacklight Squadron Leader and see if he has the location of their leader in his computer system. If he does, disable his engines or reactor and dock with him to transfer it.
entries.quest_location_d: This will take you inside Blacklight pirate territory so stay sharp and be prepared for a fight.
entries.title: Dantooine system: Inspect remaining Blacklight Pirates.
entries.title_d: We've found the location of some more Blacklight pirate scum. Disable and inspect them, if you find the location of their leader, dock and transfer that data to your ship.
